Movie Recommender System

Overview

A sleek, interactive Movie Recommender System built with Python, scikit-learn, and Streamlit.

Uses content-based filtering (TF-IDF on genres) to recommend similar movies.

Fetches real movie posters dynamically from TMDB API.

Modern, polished UI with cards, dark theme, and hover effects.

Perfect for portfolio showcase or interview demo.

Features

‚úÖ Recommend Top 5 movies based on your selected favorite movie.
‚úÖ Display movie posters, titles, and release year.
‚úÖ Handles missing posters gracefully with placeholder message.
‚úÖ Dark gradient UI with responsive movie cards.
‚úÖ Fast caching of poster images for smooth performance.

Tech Stack

Language: Python 3.x

Libraries: pandas, scikit-learn, requests, streamlit

Dataset: MovieLens 100k

API: TMDB (The Movie Database) for poster images

